00:16:20,781 --> 00:16:23,084
And you and me aren't
supposed to starve.

389
00:16:23,117 --> 00:16:24,318
We need money for food.

390
00:16:25,086 --> 00:16:26,654
Was any of that true?

391
00:16:26,687 --> 00:16:28,256
Yeah.

392
00:16:28,289 --> 00:16:29,690
We're not going to Mt. Rushmore.

393
00:16:36,064 --> 00:16:37,165
I can't discharge people

