00:18:46,894 --> 00:18:48,762
You sure?

442
00:18:48,796 --> 00:18:50,398
It... It's safe for me to go home?

443
00:18:52,366 --> 00:18:53,467
I don't know what to say.

444
00:18:53,501 --> 00:18:55,636
You'll learn.

445
00:18:55,669 --> 00:18:56,704
By doing.

