00:19:56,397 --> 00:19:58,766
I can't see anywhere where this
tumor hasn't encased her arteries.

459
00:19:58,799 --> 00:19:59,833
Claire, tell me you got something.

460
00:19:59,867 --> 00:20:01,535
I've got nothing.

461
00:20:01,569 --> 00:20:03,904
This tumor is way bigger
than it looked on the scans.

462
00:20:03,937 --> 00:20:04,905
