519
00:23:43,158 --> 00:23:46,728
so...yeah, unfortunately it seems I do.

520
00:23:46,761 --> 00:23:48,463
Okay, we can talk another time.

521
00:23:48,497 --> 00:23:49,598
Glassman talked to you?

522
00:23:52,267 --> 00:23:54,436
I don't have a problem
with an autistic doctor.

